    public class SaStepImpl
extends GaStepImpl
implements SaStep
    An implementation of the model object 'Sa Step'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Base Behavioral Feature
    • Deadline
    • Spare Cap
    • Sch Slack
    • Preempt T
    • Ready T
    • Nonpreemption Blocking
    • Shared Res
    • Self Suspension Blocking
    • Number Self Suspensions
